reviewText: I've always loved horror movies and this one's really good, I keep watching it over & over...I'm not going to spoil it for anyone but you'll be surprised at who the killer is. If you love horror movies than this is a must have:)

there are coinslot buttcracks, and mastercard swipe buttcracks...but when a girl gets out of a pool her bikini bottoms fall down and show a buttcrack big enough to find 3 lost hikers...1 star for buttcrack lovers and 1 star for girls-in-peril horror fans...
Terrible movie. Horrible acting, story was okay but not great and just an overall boring horrible movie.
